The paper discusses the use of t-SNE for visualizing high-dimensional datasets and models, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision research (cs.LG, cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of t-SNE for visualizing neural network activations and GloVe embedding vectors, which are both related to artificial intelligence and natural language processing (cs.AI, cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of GPU acceleration to improve the performance of t-SNE, which is a topic in computer engineering and parallel computing (cs.NE).
